{"tid":843271,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★【助蝗？】城大生奇招創業　商店租閒置地放篋","createTime":"2018-10-01T04:38:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-01T04:38:56.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9cd2f6d7750c4fbf2ddc142a68bf590fddf8efe2","tid":843271,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T04:38:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1833166/org/64fb06b1861ff998a81d71133424c7de.jpg/qZGqnlNnfIRYen9OpsfHCKZ2XxrTKhhPSaUkgUmlJIE?v=w1440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1833166%2Forg%2F64fb06b1861ff998a81d71133424c7de.jpg%2FqZGqnlNnfIRYen9OpsfHCKZ2XxrTKhhPSaUkgUmlJIE%3Fv%3Dw1440&h=de80cc34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n城大畢業生吳朗盟（Jason）曾被寄存行李問題困擾，今年初他看準商機，遂與友人創立《Freedrop免提王》為旅客提供行李寄存點，方便旅客<br />\n<br />\n「原來創業並唔是咁浪漫！」對於初出茅蘆的Jason而言，創業難度高，「經營一間公司好困難，需要資金同人脈輔助！」Jason表示，Freedrop推出平台約兩個月，現時反應不錯，他期望明年初有二百間加盟店。為了確保店家服務質素，團隊將不定時檢查店家服務時間，另外計劃研發手機應用程式，進一步推廣業務。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">何文田一間茶餐廳　行李堆積如山</span><br />\n<br />\n也有其他的小商戶，自行開拓存放拖篋服務，但卻惹阻路之嫌。早前何文田梭椏道的一間茶餐廳，亦推出寄存行李服務！不過，該店的行李堆積如山、幾乎阻擋整條行人路，恐有倒塌風險。香港01記者向茶餐廳了解，職員指只需到店內消費，就可以存放行李，至晚上七時許店舖打烊，便需取回行李。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/232194/%E6%8B%96%E7%AF%8B%E5%95%86%E6%A9%9F-%E5%9F%8E%E5%A4%A7%E7%94%9F%E5%A5%87%E6%8B%9B%E5%89%B5%E6%A5%AD-%E5%95%86%E5%BA%97%E7%A7%9F%E9%96%92%E7%BD%AE%E5%9C%B0%E6%94%BE%E7%AF%8B-%E6%B5%B7%E5%A4%96%E5%BA%97%E5%8A%A0%E7%9B%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2599%25BC%2F232194%2F%25E6%258B%2596%25E7%25AF%258B%25E5%2595%2586%25E6%25A9%259F-%25E5%259F%258E%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%25A5%2587%25E6%258B%259B%25E5%2589%25B5%25E6%25A5%25AD-%25E5%2595%2586%25E5%25BA%2597%25E7%25A7%259F%25E9%2596%2592%25E7%25BD%25AE%25E5%259C%25B0%25E6%2594%25BE%25E7%25AF%258B-%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E5%25A4%2596%25E5%25BA%2597%25E5%258A%25A0%25E7%259B%259F&d=2NKyO7fI0FiLhX2dfX1LHHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=da827f74\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/232194/%E6%8B%96%E7%AF%8B%E5%95%86%E6%A9%9F-%E5%9F%8E%E5%A4%A7%E7%94%9F%E5%A5%87%E6%8B%9B%E5%89%B5%E6%A5%AD-%E5%95%86%E5%BA%97%E7%A7%9F%E9%96%92%E7%BD%AE%E5%9C%B0%E6%94%BE%E7%AF%8B-%E6%B5%B7%E5%A4%96%E5%BA%97%E5%8A%A0%E7%9B%9F</a>"}]}